        "Next steps are: "
        (<node>
          "Complete the port"
          "Optimize the new kernel to make it as fast as Gambit can be (that's fast!)"
          "Port the library and IDE to Mac and X11 (this should be fairly fast at this point)")
        "I expect a first beta, beginning of 2008. "))
